                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " The B-10(p,alpha)Be-7 reaction was studied by means",
                " of the Trojan-Horse-Method applied to the",
                " d(B-10,alpha+Be-7)n reaction."
              ]
            }
          ],
